## Overview
ZPURCH_ORD_REPORT is a custom SAP ABAP report developed to display detailed 
Purchase Order information using ALV Grid (LVC).

The report retrieves Purchase Order header, item, vendor, and schedule line 
details from standard SAP tables and provides interactive drilldown functionality.

This project demonstrates practical knowledge of:
- ALV Reporting
- INNER JOIN
- Modular Programming (Includes)
- Interactive Events
- Hotspot Navigation


## Program Structure

ZPURCH_ORD_REPORT
|
|-- ZDATDECL   (Data Declarations)
|-- ZSCRN      (Selection Screen)
|-- ZFORMS     (Business Logic & ALV Display)


## Tables Used

EKKO  - Purchase Order Header
EKPO  - Purchase Order Item
LFA1  - Vendor Master
EKET  - Schedule Lines


## Selection Screen Fields

- Purchasing Document (EBELN)
- Created on (AEDAT)
- Purchasing Doc.Type (BSART)
- Created By (ERNAM)
- Material (MATNR)


## Main ALV Output Fields

- PO Number
- PO Date
- Created By
- Document Type
- Vendor ID
- Vendor Name
- Line Item
- Material Description
- Material Number
- Quantity
- Unit of Measure
- Net Price
- Total Amount


## Functional Features

1. Hotspot Navigation
   - PO Number is clickable.
   - Navigates to Transaction ME23 (Display Purchase Order).

2. Drilldown to Schedule Lines
   - Double-click on row to display schedule line data.
   - Data fetched from EKET table.
   - Displays second ALV with:
        * PO Number
        * Item Number
        * Schedule Line
        * Delivery Date
        * Quantity

3. Report Header
   - PURCHASE ORDER DETAILS
   - Reporting Date
   - Reporting Time
   - SAP Logo


