## Data Retrieval Logic

INNER JOIN performed between:
- EKKO (Header)
- LFA1 (Vendor)
- EKPO (Item)

Filters applied from selection screen inputs.


## How to Execute

1. Go to SE38
2. Enter Program: ZPURCH_ORD_REPORT
3. Execute (F8)
4. Enter selection criteria
5. View ALV Output


